Module scenebuilder.core
Package com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.editor.drag.source

Class DragSourceShadow

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.Parent
javafx.scene.Group
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.editor.drag.source.DragSourceShadow
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class DragSourceShadow
extends javafx.scene.Group
A shadow is the following construct: Group ImageView snapshot of a 'scene graph node' Region glass area with css styling Layout bounds of the group must be equal to layout bounds of the scene graph node. We ensure this by setting layoutX/Y on the image view and the region (1).
